Marketing/Advertising Manager
Confidential Company - ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 09:43:39
Ref. JB3047038
Job Description
The successful candidate will have the opportunity to drive the growth of an exciting luxury/lifestyle publication, as well as develop a portfolio of events and other publishing titles.
Flexible working environment which places a premium on teamwork.
Hired candidates can look forward to a rewarding career in the luxury lifestyle industry, with opportunities for travel abroad.
Skills
Must have bilingual skills (English and Arabic) and established contacts in the luxury sector in the UAE, and GCC countries, with a minimum 3 years experience working in the print/online publishing industry.
